Fig. 4
E–F). Masticatory processes apparently bear ca 60 denticles. Radula formula is 36 × 1–13.1.13–1 (
paratype
21 mm
), 41 × 1–12.1.12–1 (
paratype
27 mm
), 37 × 1–13.1.13–1 (
paratype
35 mm
